{"tid":1610174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 10月6日 6區黨鐵商場和你Shop","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:58:55.000Z","uid":61886,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"7292184f1f30b8e9ed5a2e12ebe7e42e4d9df645","tid":1610174,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"今日101大戰過後 超過180位手足被捕<br />\n加上地區遊行損失手足不少<br />\n<br />\n所以個人建議 <br />\n10月6日 涼住冷氣一齊去黨鐵商場window shopping<br />\n跳閘好<br />\n破壞黨鐵都好<br />\n都未對準到黨鐵春袋<br />\n我地要黨鐵每個星期日商場都收皮<br />\n睇下邊個跪低先<br />\n<br />\n6區同步和你Shop<br />\n日期：10月6日 星期日<br />\n時間：中午1點正 <br />\n活動：流動式window shopping<br />\n對像：一家大細<br />\n目標：全商場關門，然後自由活動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1x29yA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1x29yA.jpg&h=cd184980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍區<br />\n九龍灣 - 德福<br />\n佐敦 - 圓方<br />\n<br />\n新界區<br />\n青衣 - 青衣城<br />\n將軍澳 - PopCorn<br />\n沙田 - 連城<br />\n荃灣 - 綠楊坊<br />\n<br />\n剩低黨鐵商場都較少型<br />\n同人流較少<br />\n無謂分散手足<br />\n<br />\n支線 <br />\n商場內美心集團店舖、吉野家、金拱門、其他中資機構等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死一隻狗<br />\n對政權既撼動<br />\n並唔夠地產商同政府講既一句說話<br />\n<br />\n一齊攬炒經濟吧<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us."},{"pid":"85a6f16566e36692528f3658fe0c7a69a2d10777","tid":1610174,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"推 1"},{"pid":"239a3dc50f64fd029e5cf9bf73523cb998951e89","tid":1610174,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"推 2"},{"pid":"a383aed7d3f97ff8dcd66d545de69ee1b65e52e6","tid":1610174,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"推 3"},{"pid":"4801bbdd79f9523be5f4b602038fc0279b4b3732","tid":1610174,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"b6abb67285715024cb4e1620d0f52698c63608df","tid":1610174,"uid":25558,"